snippet: Sweden, the defending champion, prevailed in a shootout to edge the Czech Republic, 4-3, at the world championship in Minsk, Belarus.
abstract: Sweden's national ice hockey team defeats Czech Republic, 4-3, in shootout, at the world championship in Minsk, Belarus; other tournament results noted.
lead_paragraph: Sweden, the defending champion, prevailed in a shootout to edge the Czech Republic, 4-3, at the world championship in Minsk, Belarus.
